    <section class="about">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
            <p>At Bistro Elegance, we believe that exceptional dining is an art form that engages all the senses. Our philosophy centers around three key principles: sourcing the finest seasonal ingredients, honoring culinary traditions while embracing innovation, and creating a warm, sophisticated atmosphere where memories are made.</p>
            
            <p>Each dish tells a story of its origins, from the local farmers who grow our produce to the artisanal producers who supply our cheeses and meats. We seek to create meaningful connections between our guests and the food they enjoy, celebrating the rich tapestry of flavors that define our region's culinary landscape.</p>
            
            <img src="/api/placeholder/800/400" alt="Restaurant Interior" style="width: 100%; margin: 30px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
            
            <h2>From Farm to Table</h2>
            <p>Our commitment to sustainability drives everything we do. We work directly with local farmers who practice sustainable agriculture, ensuring that our ingredients are not only delicious but also responsibly sourced. Our menu changes with the seasons, showcasing the best that each harvest has to offer.</p>
            
            <p>By minimizing our carbon footprint and reducing food waste, we strive to be stewards of the environment while delivering an exceptional dining experience. Our kitchen team regularly visits our partner farms to strengthen these relationships and gain inspiration for new dishes.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    
